text: Chloe Woodruff (born July 21, 1987) is an American cross-country cyclist. She placed 14th in the women's cross-country race at the 2016 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1987 births Category:Living people Category:American female cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of the United States Category:Cyclists at the 2016 Summer Olympics
